429
00:47:22,570 --> 00:47:24,660
Tuyệt lắm.

430
00:47:25,120 --> 00:47:28,490
- Và sau đó thì sao?
- Chúng ta bắt đầu khoan mỏ.

431
00:47:31,710 --> 00:47:35,390
Đó là 1 nghi lễ đơn giản, Daniel,
nhưng nó rất quan trọng.

432
00:47:35,540 --> 00:47:38,410
